WEBVTT

00:06.000 --> 00:12.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:35.400 --> 01:37.026
Magnificent, aren't they?

01:37.944 --> 01:39.779
God's tears.

01:42.240 --> 01:43.658
Yeah.

01:44.242 --> 01:45.910
It's beautiful.

01:45.993 --> 01:47.829
So are the others.
I, uh...

01:49.205 --> 01:53.167
I guess I just...
have to make the right decision.

01:54.377 --> 01:57.088
In the end, it's not your eye
that must decide.

01:58.381 --> 01:59.531
Yeah.

02:10.435 --> 02:11.769
Did Rebecca call?

02:11.853 --> 02:15.106
Yeah. She'll be at the restaurant
in an hour to take you to the airport.

02:15.189 --> 02:18.693
I put your tickets, passport, and
your new cell phone in your briefcase

02:18.776 --> 02:20.403
and Hong will be there
in ten minutes.

02:20.486 --> 02:22.488
Thanks. See you in four days.

02:22.572 --> 02:23.740
The second you land,

02:23.781 --> 02:26.951
those guys are gonna start poking
and prodding to see what you're made of.

02:27.034 --> 02:29.036
Are you sure I'm the right guy
for this, Walter?

02:29.120 --> 02:32.373
I'm no good at this corporate stuff,
I hate flying...

02:32.457 --> 02:34.083
And isn't this Bob's thing, anyway?

02:34.167 --> 02:36.502
Bob? Come on, you're gonna be fine.

02:36.586 --> 02:38.254
Just don't eat anything
that wears a collar,

02:38.296 --> 02:41.048
and if you need me, I'll be on the beach
in Cozumel screening my calls.

02:42.091 --> 02:45.052
Look... this is a big break for you.

02:45.136 --> 02:48.973
But I'm giving you this account because
I think you're the right man for the job.

02:49.057 --> 02:51.392
Besides, you're gonna be a member
of the family soon, right?

02:52.685 --> 02:53.936
Going down, please.

02:56.230 --> 02:58.900
Oh. Matthew, keep away
from the bang-bang girls

02:58.983 --> 03:00.777
or Rebecca will kick my ass, all right?

03:14.373 --> 03:15.523
Matty.

03:16.584 --> 03:18.961
- Matty!
- Luke! Hey, man.

03:19.045 --> 03:21.214
- How are you, man?
- I'm good. How are you?

03:21.297 --> 03:24.258
Really good. Really good.
Good to see you. You look great.

03:24.342 --> 03:26.010
Thanks, man. I mean, I do.

03:26.094 --> 03:28.262
You still doing that whole
advertising thing in New York?

03:28.888 --> 03:30.056
I moved back.

03:30.139 --> 03:32.308
- When did you get back?
- Two months ago.

03:32.392 --> 03:34.060
Two months? What are you doing?

03:34.143 --> 03:36.479
You don't call your friend?
You could've called me.

03:36.521 --> 03:39.524
I know. I just... I moved back
with a girl that I met in New York

03:39.607 --> 03:41.692
and I'm working for her brother,
and it's...

03:41.776 --> 03:43.486
That sounds serious.

03:44.445 --> 03:46.155
Maybe. I don't know.
We'll see.

03:46.239 --> 03:48.574
You look very serious.
Look at you.

03:48.658 --> 03:49.992
I know, man.

03:50.034 --> 03:51.202
Hold on!

03:51.285 --> 03:53.329
Listen, man,

03:53.413 --> 03:55.581
Yeah, I need to probably
move my car, too.

03:55.665 --> 03:57.208
And then I'm going to China tonight.

03:57.291 --> 03:59.460
- China? That's weird.
- Yeah, I know.

03:59.544 --> 04:01.337
Let me give you a call
when I get back. Monday?

04:01.421 --> 04:03.256
Yeah, sounds good... shut up!

04:03.339 --> 04:07.385
All right, look, here's my card.
Don't wait two years... call me!

04:07.468 --> 04:08.618
The old shop.

04:08.678 --> 04:10.054
- All right?
- I will, man.

04:10.138 --> 04:11.639
You look good.
That's a nice tie.

04:11.723 --> 04:12.765
Good to see you.

04:12.849 --> 04:15.143
Are you done? Come on!

04:23.776 --> 04:26.738
He's very impressed
with what you've done,

04:26.779 --> 04:30.283
and he assures you
that when you get to China,

04:30.366 --> 04:33.619
you'll be met with much enthusiasm
and support.

04:33.703 --> 04:35.705
Thank you very much.

04:36.497 --> 04:39.167
Some champagne, please.
Excuse me.

04:46.591 --> 04:48.092
Excuse you.

04:48.968 --> 04:52.972
Matthew is a, uh, photographer.
Beautifully, wonderfully creative man.

04:53.056 --> 04:55.016
And here's my favorite sister.

04:55.099 --> 04:56.601
His only sister.

04:57.935 --> 05:00.980
Mr. Hong, Ms. Chin,
this is my sister Rebecca.

05:06.611 --> 05:08.112
Hey, Sweetie. How are you?

05:08.196 --> 05:09.363
As you can see,

05:09.447 --> 05:12.408
Matthew has managed to make himself
indispensable even away from the office.

05:17.455 --> 05:20.792
Here, Sweetie. Just take one of these,
to help you sleep on the plane.

05:20.875 --> 05:23.377
Mr. Hong would like
to propose a toast.

05:23.461 --> 05:24.611
Oh, yes.

05:27.381 --> 05:31.094
To a long and prosperous marriage...

05:31.135 --> 05:32.845
of our two companies.

05:32.929 --> 05:34.097
Are you okay?

05:34.138 --> 05:35.765
Yeah.

05:35.807 --> 05:38.351
Um, excuse me.

05:38.434 --> 05:39.602
I'll be right back.

05:40.686 --> 05:42.355
Excuse me,

06:01.207 --> 06:02.792
Just a minute!

06:02.875 --> 06:04.377
Sorry.

06:27.024 --> 06:29.694
No, you listen!
And I don't feel like calming down.

06:29.777 --> 06:32.780
It's over, okay?
That's why I wanted to meet.

06:34.699 --> 06:37.118
No, actually I don't think
it was an accident.

06:41.622 --> 06:42.790
It's in the paper!

06:45.168 --> 06:46.753
I don't ever want
to see you again, Daniel.

06:49.297 --> 06:52.008
Stop following me,
or I'll call the police!

06:54.218 --> 06:55.386
Lisa.

06:57.221 --> 06:58.389
Lisa!

07:01.434 --> 07:03.686
Whoa. Hey, come on.

07:04.687 --> 07:06.481
Are you all right?

07:07.607 --> 07:09.442
I pissed her off.

07:10.610 --> 07:12.820
You wanna put that
on this card, please?

07:50.149 --> 07:53.403
Oh! This stupid...

07:53.486 --> 07:54.987
Need some help there, Mare?

07:55.905 --> 07:57.865
- What's up?
- It's so frustrating.

07:57.949 --> 08:00.618
I just can't work out
why there's no sound.

08:00.701 --> 08:02.036
I just...

08:22.473 --> 08:24.767
Matthew? Hello?

08:25.935 --> 08:27.395
Anybody home?

08:28.771 --> 08:31.023
I'll take this one, if you want.

08:31.107 --> 08:32.692
Knock yourself out, kid.

08:58.551 --> 08:59.886
Oh, my God.

09:03.639 --> 09:04.789
Shit.

09:07.518 --> 09:10.521
- They wanna know how long... hey!
- Mary, I'll be right back.

09:10.605 --> 09:11.939
- Sorry.
- Where are you going?!

09:12.023 --> 09:13.173
Oh, sorry!

09:37.090 --> 09:39.258
- Hey, guys.
- Hey, Lisa.

09:39.342 --> 09:41.052
See you inside.

11:24.739 --> 11:25.889
Hey.

11:26.908 --> 11:28.058
Hey.

11:28.868 --> 11:31.037
- Probably time to go, right?
- Yes.

11:31.120 --> 11:32.288
Okay.

11:38.002 --> 11:41.464
Pre-boarding call
for flight 752 to Munich.

11:41.547 --> 11:44.926
All passengers should board
at this time at gate 5-A

11:47.637 --> 11:49.597
I guess, uh, this is it.

11:49.680 --> 11:51.808
Are you sure nothing's wrong?

11:51.891 --> 11:53.142
No. No, I'm fine.

11:53.226 --> 11:54.894
Okay. Well,
call me when you get there.

11:54.977 --> 11:56.437
Okay. I will.

11:56.521 --> 11:57.671
I love you.

11:58.523 --> 11:59.673
Me, too.

12:02.193 --> 12:03.236
Bye.

12:03.319 --> 12:04.469
Bye.

12:08.699 --> 12:09.849
Your attention. Please.

12:09.909 --> 12:14.247
This is the final boarding call
for American Airlines flight 153

12:14.330 --> 12:16.290
service to Shanghai.

12:16.374 --> 12:19.585
All passengers should now
be boarding at gate 10-B.

12:22.630 --> 12:25.800
Matthew Simon.
S-l-M-O-N.

12:29.053 --> 12:30.203
Shit.

12:32.140 --> 12:33.307
Yeah.

12:34.851 --> 12:37.687
Yeah. No, he's not on the plane.

12:41.274 --> 12:42.424
He's...

12:44.485 --> 12:45.653
He's sick.

12:46.779 --> 12:49.866
No, he's very sick.
He has food poisoning.

12:50.825 --> 12:53.161
No, he'll be there

13:16.934 --> 13:18.084
Lisa?

13:27.195 --> 13:28.696
All right.

13:38.956 --> 13:40.792
Hello?

14:09.862 --> 14:11.030
Lisa?

14:54.282 --> 14:57.744
Here. Sweetie. Just take one of these
to help you sleep on the plane.

15:38.618 --> 15:42.455
That line... what it does to your calf...
That is what we call sexy.

15:43.414 --> 15:45.124
Wanna try pink? Hmm?

15:45.208 --> 15:47.043
- Okay.
- Okay. Have a seat.

15:47.126 --> 15:49.462
Hey. There you are.
Where you been?

15:49.545 --> 15:51.756
You look like shit.
I hope she was worth it.

15:51.839 --> 15:54.842
Hey, do we have
a size ten in pink?

15:54.926 --> 15:56.427
Yeah, in the back.

15:56.511 --> 15:57.804
- Hey, Ellie.
- Hey.

15:57.887 --> 15:59.555
- I gotta talk to you.
- Lady Dragon Shoes.

15:59.597 --> 16:01.599
Ow. So, who is she?

16:02.642 --> 16:03.893
You wouldn't believe me.

16:03.976 --> 16:06.312
Betcha I do. I probably even know her.
What's her name?

16:07.647 --> 16:08.815
That's the thing.

16:10.149 --> 16:12.735
You don't know her name?
Oh, man.

16:12.819 --> 16:14.362
I know that she's a dancer.

16:14.987 --> 16:16.406
You mean, like a stripper?

16:16.447 --> 16:19.283
No, shithead.

16:19.367 --> 16:21.869
Oh, God.

16:21.953 --> 16:23.663
But her face is like...

16:23.746 --> 16:25.206
Her eyes...

16:26.833 --> 16:29.460
and her... skin is just...

16:30.711 --> 16:32.255
She just makes me all...

16:32.338 --> 16:37.260
What is "wha" and "duh"? She just
makes you more inarticulate than usual.

16:37.301 --> 16:40.388
You are obsessed,

16:40.471 --> 16:43.433
I mean, I don't know how

16:43.516 --> 16:46.477
I mean, my customer over there...
She's got great legs. Ellie.

16:46.561 --> 16:49.397
All right? There is
something hot about Ellie.

16:49.480 --> 16:50.940
The blonde at the window.

16:51.023 --> 16:52.525
I mean, come on.

16:56.487 --> 16:57.655
What are you doing?

17:00.867 --> 17:02.118
Matty, are you all right?

17:02.201 --> 17:04.454
Lady Dragon Shoes.
Can I help you?

17:06.455 --> 17:08.332
The blonde?

17:14.005 --> 17:15.298
What are you doing?

17:15.339 --> 17:16.507
Give me some shoes.

17:16.590 --> 17:17.842
- Shoes?
- Yeah.

17:17.925 --> 17:19.176
Got lots of shoes.

17:25.767 --> 17:28.686
I'm sorry I took so long.
Pink. It's my last pair.

17:31.856 --> 17:33.524
Could I help you with anything?

17:35.026 --> 17:36.176
Yes.

17:37.570 --> 17:39.572
Those shoes in the window.

17:39.655 --> 17:41.491
The black ones
with the red sole.

17:41.532 --> 17:44.035
I'd like to try them on, please.

17:44.118 --> 17:45.912
The blacks and reds. Okay.

17:45.995 --> 17:48.539
I'll just go in the back
and get them for you.

17:49.707 --> 17:52.085
That's where we keep them...
In the back... so...

17:53.169 --> 17:54.337
I'll be right back.

17:54.420 --> 17:55.671
Uh, Matty?

17:55.755 --> 17:59.175
Maybe you'd like to ask the lady
what size shoe she wears.

17:59.217 --> 18:00.593
- Right.
- 8 1/2.

18:00.676 --> 18:02.512
Like Fellini.

18:02.553 --> 18:04.055
Right.

18:04.138 --> 18:09.560
I mean his movie, not his shoe size.

18:12.605 --> 18:13.773
8 1/2.

18:16.943 --> 18:17.944
Shit.

18:18.027 --> 18:19.237
What was that?

18:19.320 --> 18:20.905
Fellini! What the hell
was I thinking?

18:20.988 --> 18:22.615
I have no idea.

18:22.698 --> 18:25.743
But you were right about one thing.
God, she's beautiful.

18:25.827 --> 18:28.830
And you, my man, are an idiot.

18:28.913 --> 18:31.249
All right, look.
Here's the thing, all right?

18:31.332 --> 18:33.626
You've obviously blown it,
she obviously hates you,

18:33.709 --> 18:35.878
so you stay right here
and let the man take a shot.

18:35.920 --> 18:38.423
- Shut up. Give me the shoes.
- All right. Go.

18:38.464 --> 18:40.299
Just remember...
You're not funny.

18:46.806 --> 18:48.558
Here we go.
Black and red.

19:16.794 --> 19:18.129
What do you think?

19:20.089 --> 19:21.424
They're too big.

19:22.884 --> 19:24.218
Too big? Really?

19:25.094 --> 19:27.513
Luke, these are 91/2s.

19:28.139 --> 19:30.767
I'm sorry.
That's the smallest size we have.

19:30.850 --> 19:32.351
Oh, well. Too bad.

19:33.269 --> 19:35.730
Not... you know...
not necessarily.

19:35.813 --> 19:37.607
We can order these for you.

19:37.690 --> 19:40.485
Special order. And, uh...
I can, uh, if you leave your number,

19:40.568 --> 19:42.779
I can give you a call personally
when they come in.

19:42.820 --> 19:44.906
Do you normally spy on people?

19:46.991 --> 19:48.141
What?

19:49.327 --> 19:53.164
Are you really gonna tell me that
you're a huge fan of modern dance?

19:58.669 --> 20:02.924
Look, I've never done
anything like that before.

20:04.509 --> 20:08.805
Honestly... could you let me take you out
for a cup of coffee and explain?

20:08.888 --> 20:10.431
I don't think so.

20:10.515 --> 20:12.809
I'll stay on my side of the table.
I promise.

20:12.850 --> 20:15.061
Just call me
when the shoes come in, okay?

20:16.729 --> 20:18.981
Listen, I'm not what you
think I am. Ok?

20:25.947 --> 20:27.097
Shit.

20:36.791 --> 20:41.504
"Tomorrow night. 6:00.
Café Tangiers on Kinzie.

20:41.587 --> 20:43.589
Now you won't have to follow me."

21:04.569 --> 21:08.573
Well, my parents eventually split up,
and my mom moved back to Prague.

21:09.407 --> 21:11.826
But my dad's still here.
He lives in California.

21:13.786 --> 21:15.955
I wish I was in California right now.

21:19.000 --> 21:21.377
So, why did you want
to become a photographer?

21:25.715 --> 21:26.966
Fish.

21:27.133 --> 21:28.384
Fish.

21:30.595 --> 21:32.263
Tropical fish, actually.

21:33.890 --> 21:38.811
When I was a kid, I used to go
to the library and pick out all the books...

21:39.645 --> 21:41.355
with tropical fish, you know.

21:41.439 --> 21:44.150
Beautiful colors and shapes.

21:44.233 --> 21:47.904
When I was eight years old, I realized
someone had to take pictures of the fish.

21:47.987 --> 21:49.739
And I wanted that to be me.

21:50.490 --> 21:54.327
But I grew up and I realized that...

21:54.410 --> 21:57.371
things don't have to be extraordinary
to be beautiful.

21:57.455 --> 21:59.791
The ordinary
could be just as beautiful.

22:01.000 --> 22:02.794
Like what?

22:04.337 --> 22:05.487
Well...

22:06.089 --> 22:07.924
Like... you see the couple there?

22:09.217 --> 22:11.886
Look at the way the girl
is holding on to him so tight.

22:11.969 --> 22:14.180
But he can still drink his coffee.

22:14.263 --> 22:17.100
It looks like she feels safe
wrapped around him.

22:23.356 --> 22:25.691
And if you believe that,
I'll tell you another one.

22:33.408 --> 22:34.784
Take my picture.

22:36.202 --> 22:38.121
I feel beautiful tonight.

23:18.703 --> 23:19.853
Bye.

23:33.509 --> 23:34.659
Bye.

23:45.521 --> 23:46.671
Okay.

24:25.186 --> 24:26.854
- Hi.
- Hi.

25:26.497 --> 25:27.832
Ma'am?

25:27.915 --> 25:30.585
I have your dry cleaning.

25:32.253 --> 25:33.629
Shit.

26:08.873 --> 26:11.042
Hey, you're not in China.

26:11.125 --> 26:12.835
I didn't make it past O'Hare.

26:13.795 --> 26:15.588
- What happened?
- I found Lisa.

26:15.671 --> 26:17.256
Whoa.

26:24.222 --> 26:25.431
Here it is.

26:25.515 --> 26:27.350
This is the article she left behind.

26:28.142 --> 26:30.144
The funeral's today.

26:30.228 --> 26:32.271
I can't believe you're
blowing off Shanghai for this.

26:32.355 --> 26:34.690
This isn't actually Lisa.
This is a compact.

26:34.732 --> 26:36.943
What about your woman?
What's her name, anyway?

26:37.026 --> 26:38.194
Rebecca.

26:38.236 --> 26:39.904
Yeah, I mean, isn't...

26:41.447 --> 26:42.782
Shit.

26:44.242 --> 26:45.410
Is it broke?

26:46.994 --> 26:48.162
You superstitious?

26:48.246 --> 26:50.289
God, I am so stupid.
Here, give it to me...

26:50.373 --> 26:52.333
- No, no. It's okay.
- I'm sorry.

26:52.417 --> 26:55.086
You're right.
This doesn't make any sense.

26:55.169 --> 26:57.839
One minute I'm looking at rings,
and the next I'm here, doing this.

26:57.922 --> 27:00.716
Whoa.
Whoa, looking at rings?

27:00.758 --> 27:03.177
I didn't realize you were that serious.

27:03.261 --> 27:04.595
Apparently, I'm not.

27:05.179 --> 27:08.141
See, that's how the universe works.

27:08.224 --> 27:11.394
The minute you make a decision...
You decide on anything...

27:11.436 --> 27:13.688
Along comes temptation.

27:14.564 --> 27:15.940
What would you do?

27:17.483 --> 27:21.404
Keep them both and hope they didn't find
out about each other is what I would do.

27:21.487 --> 27:23.823
That's perfect.
Asshole.

27:28.995 --> 27:31.247
I have to find out why she left.

27:31.330 --> 27:33.166
She got scared.
Everyone gets scared.

27:33.249 --> 27:36.836
No, not Lisa. She wouldn't have
left without an explanation.

27:36.919 --> 27:39.589
Without some sort of letter
or a call or something.

27:39.630 --> 27:41.591
She's not like that.

27:41.632 --> 27:44.135
Something must've happened,
and whatever it was...

27:44.218 --> 27:46.554
Screwed you up big time.

27:51.559 --> 27:52.935
I know she loved me.

27:54.479 --> 27:56.481
So let me borrow
your keys, okay?

27:57.648 --> 27:58.798
Why?

27:59.817 --> 28:02.320
The funeral's today.
It's the only lead I've got.

28:02.403 --> 28:04.280
Oh... my car.

28:04.989 --> 28:07.366
- Come on.
- Okay. I know. I'm sorry.

28:07.450 --> 28:09.410
You just have to be back by 7:00.

28:09.494 --> 28:10.828
I will. Thank you.

28:10.912 --> 28:12.246
I've got a date.

28:14.290 --> 28:15.958
You got a date?

28:16.000 --> 28:17.168
Yeah, I got a date.

28:18.002 --> 28:19.152
With who?

28:19.212 --> 28:22.799
This actress that came into my shop
a couple weeks ago, and, uh...

28:22.840 --> 28:26.594
God, I like her a lot,

28:26.677 --> 28:29.764
I won't be. 6:00.
I'll be back by 6:00, okay?

28:36.896 --> 28:39.565
"Lisa. I've been trying to find you.

28:39.649 --> 28:42.193
I have your powder case.
Call me at..."

28:47.031 --> 28:48.074
Excuse me?

28:48.157 --> 28:50.076
What can I do for you?

28:52.370 --> 28:54.747
I found a hotel key
in the back yesterday.

28:54.831 --> 28:56.874
A woman left it.
I don't know if you saw her.

28:57.792 --> 29:00.920
She fell right over there.
Broke her heel.

29:01.003 --> 29:02.964
Yesterday?
Yeah, that's right. I remember.

29:03.047 --> 29:05.133
You wanted to leave
the keys with me?

29:05.216 --> 29:07.135
No. Actually, I, uh...

29:07.218 --> 29:09.512
could you give her this note
if she comes back in here?

29:09.595 --> 29:11.180
- No problem.
- Thanks a lot.

29:11.264 --> 29:12.414
Sure.

30:16.245 --> 30:17.395
Lisa!

30:19.123 --> 30:20.273
Lisa!

31:28.776 --> 31:31.779
"Lisa. I returned your key
as you asked.

31:31.863 --> 31:35.324
"You must let me see you
if only for one last time.

31:35.408 --> 31:37.910
"Call me.
My heart can't stand it.

31:38.661 --> 31:40.997
All my love. Daniel."

32:55.446 --> 32:56.596
Shit.

33:23.975 --> 33:25.643
- Ass.
- I'm so sorry.

33:25.727 --> 33:27.895
- Hey, I could explain.
- You are an asshole.

33:27.979 --> 33:30.106
Do me a favor...
Don't ask me for any more favors.

33:30.189 --> 33:31.858
Come on.
Luke...

33:33.317 --> 33:35.820
I found her. I think I found her.
I found her apartment, anyway.

33:35.903 --> 33:37.572
I'm really happy for you, Matty.

33:37.655 --> 33:40.616
I left a note under her door
to meet me at the park tomorrow.

33:40.658 --> 33:42.952
Guess you guys
should have a picnic.

33:43.035 --> 33:45.079
Jesus, man.

33:45.163 --> 33:47.623
My entire evening is screwed.

33:47.665 --> 33:49.709
Look, I'm not really
that late, brother.

33:49.792 --> 33:53.755
Alex doesn't wait for anyone. Trust me.
I've already left three messages.

33:54.505 --> 33:56.132
Well, why didn't you take a cab?

33:56.215 --> 33:59.051
'Cause I was waiting for you.
I was waiting for my car.

33:59.969 --> 34:02.555
Luke, it's not that late.

34:02.638 --> 34:05.892
Go over there? And do what?
Throw little pebbles up at her window?

34:06.642 --> 34:09.312
She's gone. It's over.
Just forget it.

34:11.355 --> 34:12.505
Maybe not.

34:17.820 --> 34:20.489
I hope, for our friendship,
this is who I want it to be.

34:20.531 --> 34:22.658
Want to see how cool I am?
Three rings.

34:25.411 --> 34:26.746
Hello?

34:26.829 --> 34:28.748
Hey, how's it goin'?

34:28.831 --> 34:31.501
Oh, I'm so sorry.
Did you get my messages?

34:32.502 --> 34:36.214
No, I lent my car to my buddy Matt,
and he was a little late coming home.

34:37.547 --> 34:40.384
No, sure. He's right here.
Hold on a sec.

34:40.467 --> 34:41.803
She wants to talk to you.

34:42.844 --> 34:45.181
Fix it.
You have to fix it.

34:48.893 --> 34:50.043
Hello?

34:50.645 --> 34:52.813
He's full of shit. Isn't he?

34:52.897 --> 34:54.899
Yeah, he's full of shit, all right.

34:54.982 --> 34:56.317
Yeah. I knew it.

34:57.693 --> 35:01.406
He didn't lend me his car. I took it.

35:01.489 --> 35:02.740
I stole his keys.

35:02.824 --> 35:04.325
That's good.

35:04.409 --> 35:05.910
Why would you do that?

35:07.662 --> 35:09.163
Because I'm a selfish idiot.

35:10.456 --> 35:13.292
And I had this whole thing
going on that...

35:14.419 --> 35:16.003
I don't wanna bore you with it.

35:16.087 --> 35:17.237
Please. I insist.

35:18.798 --> 35:19.948
Okay.

35:20.800 --> 35:22.969
Well, um...

35:23.928 --> 35:27.056
I was looking for somebody.
A woman.

35:28.141 --> 35:29.308
I wasn't thinking.

35:29.392 --> 35:31.227
Got a little desperate.

35:31.269 --> 35:33.104
Oh. I'm sorry.

35:33.187 --> 35:34.355
No.

35:34.439 --> 35:36.357
I should be apologizing to you.

35:37.442 --> 35:41.070
And I am apologizing to you.
I'm very sorry that I ruined your evening.

35:41.863 --> 35:43.197
Did you find her?

35:44.532 --> 35:47.577
I think so. Yeah.
I found where she lives.

35:47.660 --> 35:49.996
Well. You should go back.
And you should look for her.

35:50.788 --> 35:52.081
I think I will. Thanks.

35:52.165 --> 35:53.833
You're boring now.
Give me the phone.

35:53.916 --> 35:55.585
- Okay, Alex. I gotta go.
- Nice to talk to you.

35:55.626 --> 35:57.462
Nice to talk to you, too.
Bye-bye.

35:58.087 --> 35:59.338
She's nice, man.

35:59.422 --> 36:00.572
Thanks.

36:01.299 --> 36:02.449
Hello?

36:07.805 --> 36:10.683
Okay. Why don't I just...
I'll pick you up at the theater.

36:27.283 --> 36:29.619
I think not so, my lord.

36:29.660 --> 36:31.662
Dear lad, believe it,

36:31.746 --> 36:36.250
for they shall yet belie thy happy years
to say thou art a man.

36:36.334 --> 36:37.484
Prosper well in this,

36:37.543 --> 36:40.171
and thou shalt live as freely as thy lord
to call his fortunes thine.

36:40.254 --> 36:42.632
I'll do my best to woo your lady...

36:43.299 --> 36:45.134
and yet a barful strife.

36:45.176 --> 36:47.929
Whoe'er I woo, myself
would be his wife.

36:48.012 --> 36:50.264
Alex, what's going on?

36:52.350 --> 36:53.500
What do you mean?

36:53.559 --> 36:56.062
Well, I'm sitting in the audience
and I'm getting nothing.

36:56.729 --> 36:59.899
I figured maybe I'm missing something,
so I come, I take a closer look.

36:59.982 --> 37:02.110
But you know what?
I'm still not buying it.

37:02.193 --> 37:04.237
What the hell's
the matter with you today?

37:05.655 --> 37:09.367
Look, the line, "Whoe'er I woo,

37:09.450 --> 37:11.285
defines your character.

37:11.369 --> 37:12.745
You're in love with this guy,

37:12.829 --> 37:16.499
and he is asking you
to help him get another woman!

37:16.541 --> 37:20.670
You're upset, you're confused,
it's tearing you up inside!

37:20.711 --> 37:23.714
We've gotta see the love,
but we've also gotta see the agony.

37:24.549 --> 37:26.509
You have been in love before,

37:29.470 --> 37:31.180
Yes. Sure.

37:31.264 --> 37:35.017
Oh, good. Well, please,
share a little something with us, huh?

37:36.894 --> 37:41.274
God. You sound so close.
Can't believe you're 7.000 miles away.

37:41.357 --> 37:42.942
I know.
It's crazy, isn't it?

37:44.110 --> 37:45.778
How's the weather?

37:45.862 --> 37:47.822
I don't know.
It's still dark out.

37:47.905 --> 37:50.241
Isn't it. Like.
10: 00 in the morning there?

37:52.076 --> 37:53.411
I... you know what?

37:53.494 --> 37:57.331
I'm so zonked, I didn't

37:57.373 --> 38:00.793
you know what... it's actually a really
nice day out, now that I see it.

38:00.877 --> 38:02.712
Are you sure nothing's wrong?

38:03.588 --> 38:05.923
No. I'm just a little out of it,
that's all.

38:06.007 --> 38:09.594
Well. You better get in it. Because
today's meeting is very important.

38:09.677 --> 38:12.346
You'll be fine. Honey.
I'll speak to you later. Okay?

38:12.388 --> 38:14.223
I miss you.
Bye.

38:14.307 --> 38:15.641
Bye.

38:45.213 --> 38:48.049
"Lisa. I found your powder case.

38:48.132 --> 38:49.425
"I have to see you.

38:50.301 --> 38:52.762
"Meet me tomorrow at 3: 00.
Our usual spot.

38:53.805 --> 38:54.955
Matt."

40:06.377 --> 40:07.527
Hello?

40:17.138 --> 40:18.288
Lisa?

41:22.453 --> 41:23.603
Fuck.

42:30.021 --> 42:31.314
Lisa?

42:41.199 --> 42:43.659
Jesus Christ!
I'm sorry. It's okay.

42:43.701 --> 42:45.495
I'm calling the police!
Where's the phone?

42:45.578 --> 42:48.039
No! Don't call the police!
I'm not gonna hurt you.

42:48.122 --> 42:50.583
- Get away from me!
- Okay! Okay! Calm down!

42:50.666 --> 42:52.543
Calm down. It's okay.

42:52.627 --> 42:54.128
I'm a friend of Lisa's.

42:54.796 --> 42:56.255
A friend of Lisa's?

42:56.339 --> 42:57.507
Yeah.

42:57.548 --> 42:59.175
Is that supposed to be funny?

42:59.258 --> 43:02.929
No. You can ask her
when she comes, okay?

43:03.012 --> 43:05.890
I'm Lisa.
I live here.

43:09.185 --> 43:10.353
Your name's Lisa?

43:10.395 --> 43:11.545
Yeah.

43:14.273 --> 43:15.691
And you live here?

43:15.733 --> 43:17.068
Yeah.

43:19.987 --> 43:21.137
No...

43:23.950 --> 43:25.785
- I'm calling the cops.
- No, wait. Don't.

43:27.537 --> 43:29.122
Hey, you see that letter there?

43:32.083 --> 43:34.252
- You wrote that?
- Yeah.

43:35.128 --> 43:37.130
You were at Bellucci's on Monday.

43:39.132 --> 43:41.134
Yeah... I was.

43:41.217 --> 43:43.761
And you had a room at The Drake,
room 679?

43:44.846 --> 43:45.996
Yeah.

43:46.723 --> 43:48.307
How'd you know that?

43:54.647 --> 43:56.232
I can't believe I did this.

43:57.150 --> 43:59.193
I'm going crazy. Here.

44:00.153 --> 44:01.821
That's yours.

44:04.115 --> 44:05.265
It's broken.

44:06.117 --> 44:08.786
I'd be happy to pay for it.
You know, my bad luck.

44:09.370 --> 44:10.520
Wait.

44:11.706 --> 44:12.874
Your hand.

44:13.708 --> 44:14.959
It's bleeding.

44:16.210 --> 44:17.920
It's all right.

44:18.755 --> 44:19.797
I got this.

44:19.881 --> 44:23.217
No, I...

44:27.138 --> 44:28.288
Okay.

44:28.931 --> 44:30.081
Thank you.

44:33.811 --> 44:35.146
You know, at the restaurant,

44:35.229 --> 44:37.732
I would've bet anything
you were this girl I used to know.

44:41.110 --> 44:45.073
But now seeing you here, you don't
really look that much like her at all.

44:47.283 --> 44:48.493
Must be hallucinating.

44:51.204 --> 44:52.747
I was crazy about her.

44:58.878 --> 45:02.465
So, what about the, uh...

45:02.548 --> 45:05.551
- Daniel.
- Yeah. What's his story?

45:08.763 --> 45:10.765
He's been stalking me.

45:10.807 --> 45:13.643
He scares the hell out of me.

45:13.726 --> 45:18.064
That's why I was staying in the hotel...
Because I didn't want him to find me.

45:19.524 --> 45:21.192
I hope he didn't follow you here.

45:23.444 --> 45:25.029
I don't think so. No.

45:26.239 --> 45:27.782
How's your hand?

45:28.741 --> 45:30.243
It's okay.

45:30.326 --> 45:32.537
I wasn't even hungry or anything.

45:33.830 --> 45:35.081
Actually, you know what?

45:36.124 --> 45:37.458
Thank you for everything.

45:38.292 --> 45:39.442
For the bandage...

45:41.170 --> 45:42.964
not calling the cops...

45:43.548 --> 45:47.051
not beating me to death
with the little bronze ballerina, or...

45:49.721 --> 45:51.139
You're leaving?

45:52.181 --> 45:53.331
Yeah.

45:54.851 --> 45:56.310
I'm late, you know.

45:57.395 --> 46:00.690
Very late, actually, for China, so...

46:01.774 --> 46:03.776
China. That's funny.

46:04.861 --> 46:06.529
That's what my friend said, too.

46:09.449 --> 46:11.117
Well, maybe you should wait.

46:12.034 --> 46:15.329
I can't. I mean...
I gotta go.

46:15.371 --> 46:19.208
Do you really think planes
are still taking off this late?

46:25.089 --> 46:26.883
What are you doing?

46:30.094 --> 46:31.262
I'm scared.

46:32.305 --> 46:33.556
Of him.

46:34.849 --> 46:38.519
I haven't stayed alone here
since his wife died, and...

46:40.938 --> 46:42.440
Would you mind if you stayed?

46:45.735 --> 46:48.571
Lisa, you don't even know me.
I broke into your apartment...

46:48.654 --> 46:50.490
I know. I know. I know.

46:50.573 --> 46:54.410
But... don't take this the wrong way,
but I just think you're a nice guy.

46:54.494 --> 46:55.828
That's all.

47:03.795 --> 47:04.945
Okay.

47:06.964 --> 47:08.049
Good.

47:08.091 --> 47:09.759
Where does a nice guy sleep?

47:10.593 --> 47:13.179
A nice guy sleeps on the couch.

47:52.260 --> 47:53.594
What are you doing?

47:54.971 --> 47:56.305
I'm watching you sleep.

48:30.673 --> 48:31.823
Lisa!

48:41.684 --> 48:43.352
Hey, how are you?

48:44.062 --> 48:45.730
What are you doing here?

48:45.813 --> 48:47.148
I gotta talk to you.

48:48.066 --> 48:49.525
Now?

48:49.609 --> 48:51.277
Yeah, it's kind of important.

48:52.111 --> 48:54.947
Wanna go get a drink or something?
It's freezing out here.

48:55.031 --> 48:56.866
- Okay.
- Okay? Come on.

48:58.493 --> 49:04.123
My friend gave my stuff
to this head of the agency, and...

49:04.207 --> 49:05.374
he liked it.

49:05.416 --> 49:06.793
So...

49:06.876 --> 49:08.920
he offered me a job in New York.

49:09.003 --> 49:11.089
That's great.

49:13.424 --> 49:15.802
It'll help me pay my rent, but...

49:15.885 --> 49:17.720
But what? Why not?

49:19.180 --> 49:20.330
Move in with me.

49:23.768 --> 49:27.230
I... I know it's only been
a couple of months, but I just, um...

49:28.439 --> 49:30.525
You're the reason
I don't wanna move to New York.

49:31.984 --> 49:33.903
I wanna make my life
here with you.

49:36.864 --> 49:41.202
Look, I'm really late for rehearsal.
Can we talk about this tomorrow?

49:45.164 --> 49:46.314
Sure.

49:47.208 --> 49:49.585
Matthew, trust me, okay?

49:49.627 --> 49:52.130
Just meet me tomorrow
in the park. Same time.

49:54.757 --> 49:55.907
Bye.

50:31.210 --> 50:32.962
Have you seen Lisa?

50:33.004 --> 50:34.297
Lisa?

50:34.338 --> 50:36.340
She's gone on a European tour
of Cabaret.

50:37.175 --> 50:38.342
It all happened real fast.

50:38.426 --> 50:41.596
They came to our rehearsal and
just picked her out, and she was gone.

50:43.347 --> 50:47.685
Like... did she say anything
before she left?

50:48.394 --> 50:49.544
Like what?

50:50.563 --> 50:51.713
Like, uh...

50:55.276 --> 50:56.652
Cool. Thanks.

50:56.736 --> 50:57.886
Okay.

52:43.259 --> 52:44.409
- Hi.
- Hi.

52:54.437 --> 52:56.105
You want a cup of coffee?

52:56.189 --> 52:57.857
Yeah, sure. Thanks.

53:19.212 --> 53:20.362
No.

53:21.130 --> 53:22.280
No.

53:25.927 --> 53:27.077
No.

53:27.887 --> 53:29.037
Yeah.

53:38.981 --> 53:40.691
He broke all my cups.

53:42.902 --> 53:44.070
That's original.

53:47.907 --> 53:49.492
Sugar?

53:49.575 --> 53:51.035
Thanks. Yeah.

53:58.459 --> 53:59.609
Thank you.

54:00.253 --> 54:01.403
To us.

54:26.487 --> 54:27.637
Leaving?

54:28.239 --> 54:30.491
Yeah. I have to go to work.

54:31.784 --> 54:33.161
I'm due at the hospital.

54:34.370 --> 54:35.872
That's right.
You're a nurse.

54:35.955 --> 54:37.665
I got a double shift.

54:44.505 --> 54:46.382
You should stay.

54:50.303 --> 54:51.721
You have a key?

54:51.804 --> 54:52.954
Yeah.

54:54.182 --> 54:55.975
Well, I should be back by 10:00.

54:57.935 --> 54:59.520
Will I see you later?

55:01.939 --> 55:03.089
Maybe.

55:04.108 --> 55:05.258
Yeah.

55:13.785 --> 55:15.119
- Bye.
- Bye.

55:27.340 --> 55:29.217
You were at Bellucci's on Monday.

55:30.843 --> 55:33.262
Yeah. I was.

55:37.850 --> 55:39.000
Hello?

55:39.852 --> 55:41.354
What happened to you?

55:43.147 --> 55:45.483
Hang on.
Just a minute!

55:46.192 --> 55:48.653
Look, could I stay at your place
for a couple of days?

55:48.736 --> 55:50.571
- Yeah. Of course.
- Great.

55:50.655 --> 55:53.324
Well, I've gotta call Daniel first,
then I'll be right over.

55:53.366 --> 55:54.700
- Okay.
- Bye.

56:04.001 --> 56:05.151
Lisa!

56:08.256 --> 56:10.007
Oh, shit. Get up.

57:18.409 --> 57:19.786
You know.
At the restaurant.

57:19.869 --> 57:22.371
I would've bet anything
you were this girl I used to know.

57:23.289 --> 57:27.293
But now seeing you here. You don't
really look that much like her at all.

58:00.493 --> 58:01.869
Hi.

58:25.977 --> 58:28.813
Come on, Lisa.

58:29.856 --> 58:32.525
Don't start shit like that.
Look, I don't have time...

58:32.608 --> 58:34.277
I don't wanna talk about it anymore.

58:34.360 --> 58:36.988
Stop acting like a goddamn child
about this crap!

58:37.029 --> 58:38.990
Stop screaming at me!

58:39.031 --> 58:42.493
Lisa, what are you doing?
Jesus Christ. Be careful.

58:42.577 --> 58:45.037
It's over. Get out of my house.

58:45.079 --> 58:46.956
Stop! Enough!

58:47.039 --> 58:48.875
Get back in here now!

58:48.958 --> 58:51.127
- You're gonna kill yourself!
- Don't do it!

58:51.210 --> 58:52.837
Lisa, stop this!

58:53.421 --> 58:56.174
Is this how you deal
with your problems?

58:56.257 --> 58:58.593
Huh? You run away
and act like a child?

58:58.676 --> 59:01.679
Go home, and don't bother calling me! Ok?

59:01.721 --> 59:02.805
Hi.

59:02.889 --> 59:04.390
- Goddamnit!
- Can I come in?

59:04.474 --> 59:05.725
Of course.

59:07.810 --> 59:09.979
I'm sorry.
I hate to bother you, but, um,

59:10.063 --> 59:14.567
my... ex-boyfriend just told me
he's seeing someone else.

59:14.650 --> 59:16.486
I took a chance.
I hope you don't mind.

59:16.569 --> 59:17.987
No, not at all.

59:18.071 --> 59:20.114
Lisa, this is stupid, all right?
Come on!

59:20.198 --> 59:21.741
Go home!

59:25.036 --> 59:27.413
Excuse me, are you leaving?
I'd like to park.

59:43.805 --> 59:45.473
- Hey!
- Hey.

59:51.646 --> 59:53.606
I'm sorry I didn't call.
I, um...

59:54.399 --> 59:56.526
Don't worry.
I've just been thinking.

59:57.693 --> 59:59.028
Are you okay?

01:00:01.114 --> 01:00:02.657
I'm going to London.

01:00:02.740 --> 01:00:04.075
Why?

01:00:04.992 --> 01:00:07.161
A friend of mine
started his own company.

01:00:07.245 --> 01:00:08.746
He's asked me to choreograph.

01:00:08.788 --> 01:00:11.791
Oh, my God.
That's amazing.

01:00:11.874 --> 01:00:13.543
When do you leave?

01:00:13.626 --> 01:00:14.961
Tomorrow afternoon.

01:00:15.002 --> 01:00:16.963
Is it okay
if I stay another night?

01:00:17.004 --> 01:00:18.172
Of course.

01:00:18.256 --> 01:00:20.299
No, it has to be tonight.

01:00:20.383 --> 01:00:23.219
Well, then I'd say
the 10:15 flight to Los Angeles

01:00:23.302 --> 01:00:24.762
would be your best bet.

01:00:24.846 --> 01:00:27.014
You can catch the flight
to Shanghai from there.

01:00:27.098 --> 01:00:30.226
But there's only coach available;
Your ticket's for first.

01:00:30.309 --> 01:00:31.459
It's okay.

01:00:33.646 --> 01:00:34.796
I'll tell you what.

01:00:34.856 --> 01:00:36.858
I think I can get you an upgrade.

01:00:36.941 --> 01:00:39.610
Why don't you come back
in a few hours. Around 4:00.

01:00:39.652 --> 01:00:42.029
Something should've
opened up by then.

01:00:42.113 --> 01:00:43.263
Okay.

01:00:43.781 --> 01:00:45.616
Thank you.
See you at 4:00.

01:01:06.054 --> 01:01:08.056
The hotel thing was just stupid.

01:01:09.223 --> 01:01:11.392
I knew Daniel would find me.

01:01:14.687 --> 01:01:15.837
So...

01:01:18.024 --> 01:01:19.442
Why don't you come with me?

01:01:23.071 --> 01:01:26.324
Well, I've got great shifts
at the hospital now,

01:01:26.365 --> 01:01:28.868
and, you know...

01:01:28.951 --> 01:01:30.620
And the guy who gave you that.

01:01:31.412 --> 01:01:33.247
Yeah.

01:01:36.542 --> 01:01:38.377
Well, come on. Tell me!

01:01:40.296 --> 01:01:44.342
Last night we did it
on the sofa in the doctor's lounge.

01:01:44.425 --> 01:01:46.344
You little slut.
I'm jealous!

01:01:46.385 --> 01:01:48.888
The bad part is
I'm already seeing his best friend.

01:01:49.847 --> 01:01:51.224
Another surgeon.

01:01:52.058 --> 01:01:56.104
He's adorable and he adores me,

01:01:56.437 --> 01:02:01.526
So she had the same name,

01:02:01.567 --> 01:02:03.569
That's so hot.

01:02:03.653 --> 01:02:06.447
Or... or maybe this is creepy.

01:02:06.531 --> 01:02:08.699
I think it's a little bit of both, actually.

01:02:09.909 --> 01:02:11.059
So, did you hit it?

01:02:12.870 --> 01:02:16.541
No. Um... I slept on the couch,
you know.

01:02:16.582 --> 01:02:18.418
When I woke up
in the morning, she was gone.

01:02:18.501 --> 01:02:20.420
- But you wanted to hit it, didn't you?
- Come on.

01:02:20.503 --> 01:02:21.546
Come on.

01:02:21.629 --> 01:02:25.258
