or something. 'Cause she was awesome.

01:02:56.289 --> 01:02:59.041
It was super late
by the time she got changed.

01:03:23.274 --> 01:03:26.944
So we went out.
Had a couple drinks and a couple laughs.

01:03:26.986 --> 01:03:30.656
