01:04:05.149 --> 01:04:06.299
No.

01:04:06.943 --> 01:04:09.112
Do you mind just taking me home?

01:04:13.366 --> 01:04:14.700
- Yeah.
- Yeah?

01:04:15.493 --> 01:04:16.661
Thanks.

01:04:30.007 --> 01:04:33.678
So, I was thinking,
maybe I could go upstairs with you

01:04:33.719 --> 01:04:37.890
and I'll make you
a nice big cup of hot chocolate...

01:04:39.225 --> 01:04:41.352
put a bunch
of little marshmallows up on top.

01:04:41.436 --> 01:04:43.771
We'll watch TV and just hang out.

01:04:44.689 --> 01:04:46.274
Do you love me?

01:04:49.235 --> 01:04:50.987
I just wanna be alone.

01:04:52.405 --> 01:04:53.823
