- I'll call you.

01:04:53.906 --> 01:04:55.366
I'll call you tomorrow.

01:04:56.451 --> 01:04:58.703
Alex.
Alex, wait a second.

01:04:58.786 --> 01:05:00.246
You gotta be kidding me.

01:05:00.288 --> 01:05:02.373
This girl's unbelievable.

01:05:02.457 --> 01:05:04.041
You know what?
Don't call me, okay?

01:05:04.125 --> 01:05:06.919
Don't call me until you figure out
what you wanna do with your life,

01:05:07.003 --> 01:05:08.421
'cause I can't deal with this.

01:05:08.463 --> 01:05:11.132
Every time, it's a different story
with you, all right?

01:05:15.303 --> 01:05:16.804
Wait, I... I'm sorry.

01:05:17.638 --> 01:05:18.806
I'll call you tomorrow.

01:05:20.516 --> 01:05:21.684
God!

01:05:24.854 --> 01:05:28.191
This girl is ridiculous.

01:05:46.667 --> 01:05:47.835
Taxi!

01:06:00.640 --> 01:06:02.767
And we had sex all night.

01:06:02.809 --> 01:06:04.477
And the next morning.

01:06:04.560 --> 01:06:07.522
I made her my dad's
world-famous breakfast, and...

01:06:07.605 --> 01:06:09.273
I don't know.
It was pretty perfect.

01:06:10.900 --> 01:06:12.735
That sounds really good, man.

01:06:12.819 --> 01:06:13.969
It was pretty good.

01:06:14.028 --> 01:06:15.363
When do I get to meet her?

01:06:17.532 --> 01:06:18.682
Tonight.

01:06:19.492 --> 01:06:21.994
Yeah, tonight. Tonight is her...
She's got this play.

01:06:22.078 --> 01:06:24.580
It's the big opening.
It's Shakespeare.

01:06:25.331 --> 01:06:26.416
Shakespeare.

01:06:26.499 --> 01:06:29.585
Shakespeare. I know.
But it's supposed to be good. Trust me.

01:06:31.879 --> 01:06:33.464
I'm supposed to leave tonight.

01:06:33.548 --> 01:06:34.715
Yeah, but it's early.

01:06:34.799 --> 01:06:36.717
You can go to the play,
then get on the plane.

01:06:42.223 --> 01:06:45.893
Have you seen my compact?
You know, the silver one.

01:06:46.436 --> 01:06:48.771
No, I haven't.

01:06:51.607 --> 01:06:53.776
I hope I didn't leave it
at the hotel.

01:06:55.153 --> 01:06:57.155
It was a gift from my grandmother.

01:07:04.078 --> 01:07:05.913
Where did you get this?

01:07:07.749 --> 01:07:11.002
Um... it's surgeon number two's.

01:07:11.085 --> 01:07:12.920
He left it here last week.

01:07:14.881 --> 01:07:16.549
Oh, my God.
It's so much like...

01:07:17.967 --> 01:07:19.218
What?

01:07:22.305 --> 01:07:23.639
Matthew.

01:07:36.235 --> 01:07:38.446
So you're not getting
into too much trouble?

01:07:39.864 --> 01:07:40.907
Thanks.

01:07:40.990 --> 01:07:42.533
Take care of yourself, okay?

01:08:31.541 --> 01:08:34.042
- Come on, let me film you.
- No. You first.

01:08:34.127 --> 01:08:38.339
Come on, Alex. Are you shy? You can't
be shy if you wanna be an actress.

01:08:38.423 --> 01:08:39.465
Here.

01:08:39.549 --> 01:08:42.260
- Shakespeare?
- This is your big break.

01:08:42.343 --> 01:08:44.845
That's Shakespeare.
I can't do that. That's too hard.

01:08:44.929 --> 01:08:47.432
Haply, when I shall wed.

01:08:47.473 --> 01:08:49.975
That lord whose hand
must take my plight

01:08:50.059 --> 01:08:54.397
shall carry half my love with him,
half my care and duty.

01:08:54.479 --> 01:08:59.109
Surely I shall never marry
like my sisters to love my father all.

01:09:00.027 --> 01:09:04.615
So true, my lord.
In life... oh! I blew it.

01:09:04.657 --> 01:09:06.325
I'm sorry. That was bad.

01:09:07.660 --> 01:09:09.828
No, that was amazing.

01:09:09.912 --> 01:09:12.957
You know, the thing with acting, Alex,
is you just have to commit.

01:09:13.040 --> 01:09:14.792
Otherwise, you're just a phony.

01:09:19.546 --> 01:09:20.798
I can't hear anything.

01:09:20.881 --> 01:09:22.049
I know.

01:09:23.509 --> 01:09:24.658
That's weird.

01:09:29.098 --> 01:09:31.309
- Is it hooked up right?
- Yeah.

01:09:31.392 --> 01:09:33.144
Can you take it back?

01:09:34.353 --> 01:09:36.731
I know a place
I can get it fixed, actually.

01:09:40.443 --> 01:09:42.987
Do you believe
in love at first sight?

01:09:43.029 --> 01:09:44.322
Well, who is he?

01:09:46.448 --> 01:09:48.242
Don't even try to lie about it.

01:09:48.868 --> 01:09:51.996
I haven't met him yet.
I've just seen him.

01:09:52.080 --> 01:09:54.749
I don't think he's got a girlfriend.
I can tell.

01:09:54.832 --> 01:09:56.918
Don't wait.
The good ones go fast.

01:09:57.668 --> 01:10:01.005
Well, I gotta go get the video camera,
so I'll talk to you later.

01:10:01.047 --> 01:10:02.197
All right.

01:10:02.256 --> 01:10:05.218
Hey... promise you'll talk to him?

01:10:06.385 --> 01:10:08.513
Yeah... I'll think about it.

01:10:08.596 --> 01:10:10.139
Okay. Bye.

01:10:51.889 --> 01:10:52.932
I'll be right back.

01:10:53.015 --> 01:10:54.934
- Sorry.
- Matthew, where are you going?

01:10:55.017 --> 01:10:56.352
Sorry.

01:11:24.797 --> 01:11:27.508
My God.
It's so much like... Matthew.

01:11:29.135 --> 01:11:30.285
Don't be silly.

01:11:30.344 --> 01:11:32.805
It belongs to one of the doctors
at the hospital.

01:11:34.766 --> 01:11:36.934
Why would you think of Matthew?

01:11:43.316 --> 01:11:46.110
Could I borrow
your car again tonight?

01:11:46.194 --> 01:11:47.344
Oh, sure.

01:11:48.988 --> 01:11:50.198
Thanks, Lisa.

01:11:51.157 --> 01:11:54.285
Well, I better go.
I'll see you later.

01:11:54.368 --> 01:11:55.536
Okay.

01:12:00.333 --> 01:12:02.293
Hi, excuse me?

01:12:02.376 --> 01:12:05.963
I think I might have left a compact.
It's silver, engraved.

01:12:06.005 --> 01:12:07.507
Um, let me ask.

01:12:07.590 --> 01:12:10.843
Tony, did anyone turn in
a silver compact?

01:12:10.927 --> 01:12:12.345
No. Sorry.

01:12:12.386 --> 01:12:14.138
Okay. Thank you.

01:12:14.180 --> 01:12:15.330
Lisa?

01:12:16.849 --> 01:12:18.184
Yeah?

01:12:18.267 --> 01:12:21.979
A guy did come in here looking for you.
Said he found your keys. Oh! And...

01:12:25.149 --> 01:12:26.317
He left you this.

01:12:26.359 --> 01:12:27.652
- Thank you.
- Sure.

01:12:31.656 --> 01:12:34.325
"Lisa. I've been trying to find you.

01:12:34.367 --> 01:12:36.160
"I have your powder case.

01:12:36.244 --> 01:12:37.745
"Call me.

01:12:37.829 --> 01:12:38.996
Matthew."

01:13:29.380 --> 01:13:31.716
Hey, Luke, can I talk to you
for a second?

01:13:32.675 --> 01:13:35.011
Hey, Ellie, do me a favor.
Will you help her out?

01:13:35.094 --> 01:13:36.244
Yeah, sure.

01:13:36.304 --> 01:13:37.472
How's it goin'?

01:13:37.555 --> 01:13:39.932
Hey. I just wanna say thanks
for everything

01:13:40.016 --> 01:13:42.226
and, you know,
you've been great.

01:13:42.268 --> 01:13:44.604
What about the play?
I thought you were comin' to the play.

01:13:45.897 --> 01:13:48.566
I don't wanna miss
another flight, you know.

01:13:48.608 --> 01:13:51.360
Listen, I'll make it up to you
when I get back. I promise.

01:13:52.653 --> 01:13:53.863
Hey, taxi!

01:13:54.614 --> 01:13:57.909
You have fun tonight, though, all right?
Say hi to Alex for me, and, you know.

01:13:57.992 --> 01:13:59.952
- You're a lucky guy.
- You got plenty of time.

01:13:59.994 --> 01:14:03.331
It's the late flight. I really want you
to come to the play. Please?

01:14:03.414 --> 01:14:06.459
See, things, um... it's just not going
that well with Alex.

01:14:06.542 --> 01:14:08.795
I've been kind of
exaggerating a little.

01:14:09.337 --> 01:14:10.797
What do you mean?

01:14:10.838 --> 01:14:12.006
Well...

01:14:12.090 --> 01:14:14.425
Lying.
Uh! I've been lying!

01:14:14.467 --> 01:14:16.094
It's 'cause my life's so pathetic.

01:14:16.135 --> 01:14:17.470
No all-night marathon?

01:14:17.553 --> 01:14:19.972
God, I'm lucky if I get a kiss
