01:14:20.014 --> 01:14:23.643
So I was thinking that if you came
to the play, I think that would really help.

01:14:23.726 --> 01:14:26.437
I mean, I'd be so much more
confident with you there.

01:14:26.521 --> 01:14:29.482
And then I can go to the bathroom
and you can tell her,

01:14:29.524 --> 01:14:31.192
you know, what a great guy I am

01:14:31.275 --> 01:14:34.195
and rumor has it I'm really good
in the sack, and that, um...

01:14:34.278 --> 01:14:36.656
I'm hung like a camel...
I don't know.

01:14:38.408 --> 01:14:40.993
Please? I wouldn't ask
if it didn't mean a lot to me.

01:14:41.077 --> 01:14:44.038
- I'll be there.
- Oh, you're the best. Thanks, buddy.

01:14:44.747 --> 01:14:45.915
7:30, all right?

01:14:45.998 --> 01:14:48.126
- I got it.
- Good. There you go.

01:14:48.209 --> 01:14:49.877
- See you, brother.
- Yeah.

01:14:51.671 --> 01:14:53.005
You the man. Thanks, man.

01:14:53.089 --> 01:14:57.009
Well, you're all set.
You're on flight 1559. First class.

01:14:57.927 --> 01:14:59.077
Have a good trip.

01:15:00.054 --> 01:15:01.389
I will. Thanks a lot.

01:15:22.410 --> 01:15:24.579
Um, I'm booked in a flight
to London today.

01:15:24.662 --> 01:15:27.165
I'd like to postpone it
until tomorrow, please.

01:15:30.918 --> 01:15:33.755
Those shoes.
The black ones with the red sole.

01:15:33.838 --> 01:15:35.715
I'd like to try them on. Please.

01:16:00.865 --> 01:16:05.369
Oh, excuse me, dear. Could you tell me
how to get to this museum from here?

01:16:07.080 --> 01:16:09.582
I think it's...

01:16:11.417 --> 01:16:12.919
I think it's back here.

01:16:15.630 --> 01:16:18.007
- Let me show you. I'll walk you.
- Oh, thank you.

01:16:47.453 --> 01:16:49.038
Alex, ten minutes!

01:16:49.789 --> 01:16:51.624
This is it right up here.

01:16:53.960 --> 01:16:55.962
- Here. Keep the change.
- Thanks.

01:16:56.963 --> 01:16:58.113
Thanks.

01:17:05.096 --> 01:17:08.808
How much better that man should fall
before the lion than the wolf.

01:17:09.684 --> 01:17:12.520
The clock upbraids me
with the waste of time.

01:17:14.147 --> 01:17:17.316
Be not afraid, good youth.
I will not have you.

01:17:17.400 --> 01:17:19.402
And yet when wit and youth
is come to harvest,

01:17:19.485 --> 01:17:21.946
your wife is like
to reap a proper man.

01:17:22.029 --> 01:17:23.197
I'm right here. Sorry.

01:17:23.281 --> 01:17:24.782
There lies your way.
Due west.

01:17:24.866 --> 01:17:25.950
Excuse me.

01:17:25.992 --> 01:17:30.621
Then westward ho. Grace and
good disposition attend your ladyship.

01:17:30.663 --> 01:17:33.750
You'll nothing, madam,
to my lord by me?

01:17:36.335 --> 01:17:37.503
Stay!

01:17:38.254 --> 01:17:40.840
I prithee, tell me
what thou thinkst of me.

01:17:40.923 --> 01:17:43.426
That you do... think...

01:17:49.891 --> 01:17:52.060
Sit down.

01:17:52.143 --> 01:17:53.478
- You are...
- Sorry.

01:17:54.854 --> 01:17:56.481
Not what you are.

01:17:57.648 --> 01:17:59.108
Is that her?

01:17:59.192 --> 01:18:00.693
Yeah, that's my girl.

01:18:03.237 --> 01:18:04.822
Then think you right.

01:18:05.698 --> 01:18:07.200
I am not what I am.

01:18:07.283 --> 01:18:09.619
I would you were
as I would have you be.

01:18:10.703 --> 01:18:13.498
Would it be better,

01:18:14.248 --> 01:18:16.751
I wish it might,
for now I am your fool.

01:18:23.591 --> 01:18:24.926
You're in love with this guy.

01:18:25.009 --> 01:18:27.512
And he is asking you
to help him get another woman!

01:18:27.553 --> 01:18:30.932
You're upset. You're confused.
It's tearing you up inside!

01:18:31.891 --> 01:18:34.185
You have been in love before.
Haven't you?

01:18:43.194 --> 01:18:46.072
By my innocence, I swear,
and by my youth,

01:18:46.114 --> 01:18:49.617
I have one heart,

01:18:49.700 --> 01:18:52.703
And no woman has,

01:18:52.745 --> 01:18:55.373
mistress be of it
to save I alone.

01:18:56.124 --> 01:18:58.793
And so adieu, good madam.

01:18:58.876 --> 01:19:01.796
Nevermore will I my master's tears
to you deplore.

01:19:05.633 --> 01:19:06.843
She's good.

01:19:19.439 --> 01:19:21.566
Look, I should really get
to the airport.

01:19:21.649 --> 01:19:23.818
Yeah. Yeah.
If you have to go, go.

01:19:23.901 --> 01:19:27.780
I'm sure Alex is gonna be disappointed
she didn't get a chance to meet you.

01:19:27.864 --> 01:19:30.116
Tell her she did a great job.
And I'll see you on Monday.

01:19:30.199 --> 01:19:33.119
I will. Hey, Matt, thanks for everything.
It means a lot to me.

01:19:33.911 --> 01:19:35.580
I'm sorry you didn't find Lisa.

01:19:36.289 --> 01:19:37.582
Yeah, me, too.

01:19:39.542 --> 01:19:41.836
- I'll see you around, huh?
- All right, man.

01:20:07.904 --> 01:20:09.322
Hey, Alex.

01:20:09.363 --> 01:20:10.865
Alex, it's me.

01:20:11.824 --> 01:20:13.326
Please go away.

01:20:14.285 --> 01:20:15.787
C'mon, baby. Open the door.

01:20:15.870 --> 01:20:18.706
I don't want your friend
to see me like this.

01:20:18.790 --> 01:20:21.042
He won't. He left.

01:20:22.502 --> 01:20:26.798
What? He left?
Did I scare him away?

01:20:26.839 --> 01:20:28.591
Scare him away?
You blew him away.

01:20:28.674 --> 01:20:32.303
You blew everyone away.
You were unbelievable.

01:20:32.386 --> 01:20:33.805
He just had a plane to catch.

01:20:33.846 --> 01:20:36.849
A slow one to China.
Open the door.

01:20:37.683 --> 01:20:39.060
Did he find her?

01:20:40.019 --> 01:20:41.169
What?

01:20:42.563 --> 01:20:43.981
Your friend... did...

01:20:45.900 --> 01:20:47.402
Did he find Lisa?

01:20:49.654 --> 01:20:54.659
No, it just turned out to be some... psycho
with the same name, same everything.

01:20:54.700 --> 01:20:57.703
He slept on her couch and ran away
as fast as he could.

01:20:59.205 --> 01:21:00.355
Are you okay?

01:21:03.543 --> 01:21:05.336
Alex. You've gotta help me.

01:21:07.004 --> 01:21:08.214
What's wrong?

01:21:08.297 --> 01:21:11.342
Well, I booked this job...
A European tour of Cabaret.

01:21:11.426 --> 01:21:12.927
Oh, wow! That's fantastic!

01:21:13.010 --> 01:21:15.680
I know. Some girl broke her ankle,
I'm taking over.

01:21:15.722 --> 01:21:17.515
But listen, I can't find Matthew.

01:21:17.557 --> 01:21:21.728
I've been looking all over for him,
and my plane's leaving in two hours.

01:21:21.811 --> 01:21:23.813
Did you leave him a message?

01:21:23.896 --> 01:21:26.357
I can't really leave this
on his machine, you know.

01:21:26.441 --> 01:21:28.192
It's too complicated.

01:21:28.276 --> 01:21:31.028
I wrote him a letter.
Do you mind giving it to him?

01:21:32.864 --> 01:21:35.700
I've never even met him.
He doesn't know who I am.

01:21:35.742 --> 01:21:39.078
It doesn't matter... just tell him
you're my friend. It'll be fine.

01:21:39.162 --> 01:21:41.581
You know what,

01:21:41.622 --> 01:21:44.792
just let yourself in
and leave it on his bed.

01:21:46.753 --> 01:21:49.589
I really appreciate this.
Thank you so much.

01:21:49.672 --> 01:21:51.591
Sure. Okay.

01:21:51.674 --> 01:21:52.824
All right.

01:21:56.846 --> 01:21:58.556
He asked me to move in with him.

01:22:00.558 --> 01:22:02.935
Oh. What did you say?

01:22:03.019 --> 01:22:04.562
I didn't really say anything.

01:22:04.645 --> 01:22:07.815
I was late for a class,

01:22:08.649 --> 01:22:12.111
I said I'd meet him tomorrow.
If I don't show up, you know, he'll go nuts.

01:22:12.153 --> 01:22:13.738
Anyway, I have to go.

01:22:13.780 --> 01:22:16.616
Thanks again, and I'll call you
when I get there, okay?

01:22:16.699 --> 01:22:18.826
Are you gonna do it?

01:22:19.869 --> 01:22:22.121
Of course.
I love him.

01:22:24.165 --> 01:22:25.315
Bye.

01:22:25.416 --> 01:22:26.566
Bye.

01:22:59.534 --> 01:23:02.703
Hey. This is Matthew.
Please leave a message.

01:23:03.830 --> 01:23:06.582
Hey. It's me again.

01:23:07.458 --> 01:23:08.918
Where are you?

01:23:09.001 --> 01:23:11.003
Did you get my letter?

01:23:11.087 --> 01:23:12.755
Anyway. I'm in Paris.

01:23:12.839 --> 01:23:15.925
I'm at the hotel. You got
the number in my last message.

01:23:16.008 --> 01:23:18.302
Matt. Please call me.

01:23:18.386 --> 01:23:21.180
This is driving me crazy.
I need to speak to you.

01:23:22.348 --> 01:23:25.393
Look. If you're angry at me.
Then don't be.

01:23:26.144 --> 01:23:29.021
Just call... please.
Bye.

01:24:09.896 --> 01:24:11.856
I don't know
if I can stay with the show.

01:24:11.939 --> 01:24:14.025
I feel like I have to come home
and look for him.

01:24:15.151 --> 01:24:16.486
No, I...

01:24:18.571 --> 01:24:20.865
I wasn't gonna say
anything before, but...

01:24:22.283 --> 01:24:24.494
when I brought him the letter...

01:24:25.661 --> 01:24:27.663
he wasn't expecting me, and...

01:24:30.333 --> 01:24:33.336
I found him in bed
with another woman, Lisa.

01:24:37.632 --> 01:24:39.217
I... I can't believe it.

01:24:40.760 --> 01:24:43.137
Just... forget about him.

01:24:43.221 --> 01:24:46.349
The best thing for you to do
is stay with the show and...

01:24:46.432 --> 01:24:47.725
just forget him.

01:24:52.230 --> 01:24:54.565
I really thought I knew him.

01:24:54.607 --> 01:24:57.110
Just forget him.
He's not even worth it.

01:25:11.290 --> 01:25:13.459
Luke, I'm so sorry.

01:25:13.543 --> 01:25:16.337
No. Shh... it's okay.

01:25:16.421 --> 01:25:18.089
I'm so sorry.

01:25:18.131 --> 01:25:21.092
No. Please, don't apologize.
Please. God.

01:25:23.970 --> 01:25:25.763
I know you're doing the best you can.

01:25:26.806 --> 01:25:27.956
I just...

01:25:32.395 --> 01:25:35.565
I just want you to know that I...
that I love you.

01:25:38.860 --> 01:25:41.279
All right? And I don't
wanna play games anymore.

01:25:41.320 --> 01:25:43.948
What's the point?
I'm just terrible at them anyway.

01:26:40.213 --> 01:26:42.215
Do me a favor.
Grab that, would you?

01:26:45.635 --> 01:26:46.844
Hello?

01:26:48.054 --> 01:26:49.204
Hello?

01:26:49.263 --> 01:26:51.682
- Who's this?
- Who's this?

01:26:51.724 --> 01:26:53.726
This is Matthew.
Who is this?

01:26:55.561 --> 01:26:56.938
Hello?

01:26:57.605 --> 01:26:58.689
Hello?

01:26:58.731 --> 01:27:01.818
Hey, what's up, kid?
I thought you left.

01:27:02.610 --> 01:27:04.070
No, uh...

01:27:05.446 --> 01:27:06.948
What are you still doing here?

01:27:07.031 --> 01:27:09.033
I'm over at the...

01:27:09.117 --> 01:27:10.451
girl's apartment.

01:27:11.285 --> 01:27:13.788
You went back
to the crazy girl's house?

01:27:14.747 --> 01:27:16.374
What the hell are you doing there?

01:27:19.377 --> 01:27:21.712
I'm really starting
to worry about you, man.

01:27:23.047 --> 01:27:24.882
I'm starting to worry myself.

01:27:26.592 --> 01:27:28.094
It's not just that.

01:27:28.678 --> 01:27:30.763
I couldn't even
get on the airplane.

01:27:33.975 --> 01:27:35.143
The thing is...

01:27:36.853 --> 01:27:38.563
there's something
about this apartment.

01:27:44.444 --> 01:27:46.279
It's like Lisa's been here.

01:27:47.488 --> 01:27:50.825
I know this sounds insane. But...

01:27:50.908 --> 01:27:53.077
I think this is her place. Man.

01:27:56.122 --> 01:27:58.791
Well. Maybe you're
just hot for this crazy girl.

01:27:58.875 --> 01:28:02.211
First thing you gotta do is get out
of her apartment and get over here.

01:28:02.295 --> 01:28:04.088
I'll tell you about some stuff. Too.

01:28:04.130 --> 01:28:08.259
I've had the most amazing night
of my entire life last night.

01:28:08.301 --> 01:28:11.471
Okay. I'll be over. Just give me
a couple of minutes. Okay?

01:28:11.554 --> 01:28:13.890
All right. I'll wait.
Later.

01:28:20.855 --> 01:28:22.857
- Hello?
- Hi. um...

01:28:22.940 --> 01:28:25.359
May I speak to Matthew, please?

01:28:27.528 --> 01:28:28.821
Who is this?

01:28:28.905 --> 01:28:31.324
Um... this is Lisa.

01:28:31.365 --> 01:28:34.660
I'm a friend of his.
I'm calling about my compact.

01:28:34.744 --> 01:28:36.412
I think he might have found it.

01:28:36.496 --> 01:28:38.414
Uh... which Lisa is this?

01:28:38.498 --> 01:28:39.791
Pardon me?

01:28:41.667 --> 01:28:43.628
Uh... I'll tell you what...

01:28:43.669 --> 01:28:48.007
He's actually supposed to be here
in a couple of minutes.

01:28:55.848 --> 01:28:56.998
Hello?

01:28:57.058 --> 01:28:58.208
Hello!

01:28:59.143 --> 01:29:00.293
Hi.

01:29:00.353 --> 01:29:01.503
Hi.

01:29:02.647 --> 01:29:04.816
I'm sorry I didn't come back.
My, um...

01:29:05.983 --> 01:29:09.904
double shift turned into a triple,
and I just couldn't get away.

01:29:09.987 --> 01:29:11.823
That's okay.
Don't worry about it.

01:29:12.740 --> 01:29:13.908
Are you mad?

01:29:15.034 --> 01:29:17.286
No. Not at all.
I had a great time.

01:29:18.079 --> 01:29:19.330
Where are you?

01:29:19.414 --> 01:29:22.750
Well, I'm still at work but, um,

01:29:22.834 --> 01:29:24.168
so why don't you wait?

01:29:25.503 --> 01:29:26.712
Yeah, I'll wait.

01:29:26.796 --> 01:29:29.132
Okay. Great.
I'll see you soon.

01:29:31.342 --> 01:29:36.389
Let me. Uh...
let me grab your phone number

01:29:36.472 --> 01:29:39.851
and I will have him call you
when he gets in.

01:29:39.934 --> 01:29:45.606
Um, you know... actually, could you
just tell him to meet me at 3:00?

01:29:45.690 --> 01:29:48.526
He'd know where.
Um, I'll be waiting for him.

01:29:48.568 --> 01:29:50.862
3:00. Okay.

01:29:50.945 --> 01:29:54.198
I... you know what,
it can't be him already,

01:29:54.240 --> 01:29:55.742
but I'm expecting him.

01:29:55.825 --> 01:29:58.411
Someone's at my front door.
So maybe it is him.

01:29:58.494 --> 01:29:59.829
So hold on a second.

01:30:07.086 --> 01:30:08.921
Matthew, trust me, okay?

01:30:10.381 --> 01:30:12.425
Meet me tomorrow in the park.
Same time.

01:30:15.595 --> 01:30:16.745
Bye.

01:30:25.438 --> 01:30:27.690
Yeah. I'm sorry.
It wasn't him. It was someone else.

01:30:27.774 --> 01:30:32.028
But I promise you
I will give him your message. Okay?

01:30:32.111 --> 01:30:33.821
Oh. Okay. Thank you.

01:30:39.786 --> 01:30:41.913
I went to get cigarettes.
What's going on?

01:30:43.289 --> 01:30:45.750
Matthew. He didn't leave.

01:30:45.833 --> 01:30:48.669
He went back to that girl's house.
The crazy one.

01:30:48.753 --> 01:30:50.713
Oh, the plot thickens.

01:30:50.797 --> 01:30:52.882
Oh, yeah. It gets even better.
Listen to this.

01:30:52.965 --> 01:30:56.761
So I hang up the phone,
and five seconds later, Lisa called.

01:30:58.179 --> 01:31:01.516
The real Lisa.
The one from two years ago.

01:31:01.599 --> 01:31:02.934
She wants to see him.

01:31:05.478 --> 01:31:06.729
You tell him?

01:31:06.813 --> 01:31:09.732
No, not yet.
I'll wait till he gets here.

01:31:09.816 --> 01:31:12.777
He's gonna be so happy,
he's gonna hit the moon again.

01:31:12.860 --> 01:31:14.028
I have to go!

01:31:14.695 --> 01:31:16.864
- What do you mean?
- I'll call you later. I promise.

01:31:16.948 --> 01:31:19.283
But I made breakfast.
My dad's famous potatoes.

01:31:26.666 --> 01:31:29.043
Lisa called.
She wants to see him.

01:31:31.421 --> 01:31:33.548
So, will you let me
meet your friends?

01:31:33.631 --> 01:31:35.299
Don't you have a store to run?

01:31:35.341 --> 01:31:36.968
Oh, okay.
I can take a hint.

01:31:37.009 --> 01:31:38.636
So we're going out tomorrow, right?

01:31:38.719 --> 01:31:40.722
- 7:00?
- Sure.

01:31:40.805 --> 01:31:41.848
Okay.

01:31:41.931 --> 01:31:44.016
Bye, and thanks for the lift.

01:31:44.100 --> 01:31:45.250
Bye.

01:31:47.854 --> 01:31:49.522
Matty. Hey.
Matty!

01:31:50.606 --> 01:31:52.984
- Matty!
- Luke! Hey, man!

01:31:53.067 --> 01:31:55.319
- How are you, man?
- I'm good. How are you?

01:31:55.403 --> 01:31:56.571
Really good. Really good.

01:32:03.619 --> 01:32:06.873
Oh, excuse me. Could I order an espresso
while I wait for my friend?

01:32:06.956 --> 01:32:08.106
Absolutely.

01:32:14.756 --> 01:32:17.717
He's very impressed
with what you've done.

01:32:17.759 --> 01:32:21.387
And he assures you that
when you get to China...

01:32:22.388 --> 01:32:24.682
with much enthusiasm
and support.

01:32:25.975 --> 01:32:27.477
I'm sitting over here.

01:32:29.353 --> 01:32:30.503
Excuse me. Champagne.

01:32:38.071 --> 01:32:39.221
Excuse you.

01:32:41.657 --> 01:32:42.807
No.

01:32:44.744 --> 01:32:46.913
Uh, Miss Chin,

01:32:49.874 --> 01:32:51.334
Shit, shit, shit!

01:32:51.417 --> 01:32:53.586
As you can see, uh...

01:32:56.798 --> 01:32:58.132
Here, Sweetie...

01:33:08.434 --> 01:33:10.061
Hello. Bellucci's.
May I help you?

01:33:10.103 --> 01:33:12.188
Hello, may I speak
to my friend Lisa, please?

01:33:12.271 --> 01:33:15.066
She's the blonde.
She's sitting at a table behind the bar.

01:33:16.692 --> 01:33:17.860
Yes. Just a minute. Please.

01:33:17.944 --> 01:33:20.613
Excuse me. Are you Lisa?

01:33:21.447 --> 01:33:22.490
Phone's for you.

01:33:22.573 --> 01:33:25.493
It's a little noisy here. Why don't you
take the house phone around the corner.

01:33:25.576 --> 01:33:26.744
Okay. Thank you.

01:33:26.828 --> 01:33:31.791
To a long and prosperous marriage...
of our two companies.

01:33:32.917 --> 01:33:35.378
Excuse me. I'm gonna go make
a phone call. I'll be right back.

01:33:35.461 --> 01:33:36.611
No.

01:33:38.840 --> 01:33:39.924
No.

01:33:39.966 --> 01:33:42.468
- Hello?
- Hey, Lisa. It's me.

01:33:42.552 --> 01:33:43.886
Hey. What happened to you?

01:33:43.970 --> 01:33:46.097
I know. I'm so sorry.
I got stuck at work.

01:33:46.180 --> 01:33:48.599
Look. Daniel's found me
at the hotel.

01:33:48.683 --> 01:33:50.518
Hang on.
Just a minute!

01:33:52.478 --> 01:33:55.148
Look, could I stay at your place
for a couple of days?

01:33:55.231 --> 01:33:57.066
Yeah, of course. Um...

01:33:57.984 --> 01:34:00.361
Go there right now.
I'll... I'll meet you there.

01:34:18.004 --> 01:34:19.154
Hey.

01:34:19.213 --> 01:34:20.363
Hey.

01:34:23.593 --> 01:34:24.677
How are you, Lisa?

01:34:24.761 --> 01:34:27.346
Good. How are you?

01:34:27.430 --> 01:34:28.580
Good.

01:34:30.349 --> 01:34:31.976
Thought you'd be in China by now.

01:34:32.852 --> 01:34:34.771
That makes two of us.
Sit down.

01:34:38.357 --> 01:34:40.485
- What's that?
- It's a present.

01:34:40.568 --> 01:34:42.153
- For me?
- Yeah.

01:34:44.072 --> 01:34:47.492
I saw that yours were...
Yours were broken, so...

01:34:49.118 --> 01:34:50.411
Uh, wanna try them on?

01:34:53.748 --> 01:34:55.833
That's very sweet.
You didn't have to do that.

01:34:55.875 --> 01:34:57.168
Oh, that's okay.

01:35:05.134 --> 01:35:06.302
They're a little big.

01:35:09.389 --> 01:35:11.432
What size shoe do you wear?

01:35:15.645 --> 01:35:16.795
Seven.

01:35:18.564 --> 01:35:20.191
These are 8 1/2.

01:35:27.949 --> 01:35:32.036
I would've told you what size I was if I
knew you were gonna get me some shoes.

01:35:33.121 --> 01:35:34.872
It's okay.
I could exchange them.

01:35:39.752 --> 01:35:41.295
You don't have to do that. I...

01:35:42.046 --> 01:35:45.299
Anyway, I told a friend of mine I'd
meet him for coffee before I left, so...

01:35:46.759 --> 01:35:48.428
What? You're leaving?

01:35:49.554 --> 01:35:50.722
Yeah.

01:35:52.932 --> 01:35:54.082
Bye.

01:36:12.452 --> 01:36:14.996
Hey, Luke. It's me.
Let's meet.

01:36:44.650 --> 01:36:45.985
Jesus Christ.

01:36:46.069 --> 01:36:48.029
What are you doin'?
I thought you were comin' by.

01:36:48.112 --> 01:36:51.449
I, uh... I was comin' by.
I just lost track of the time.

01:36:51.491 --> 01:36:54.160
I got good news for you.
Let's go have a drink.

01:36:54.243 --> 01:36:56.079
I want you to meet someone.
Come on.

01:36:58.289 --> 01:36:59.439
Come on.

01:37:04.921 --> 01:37:08.424
Hey, babe. I came as soon as you called.
Look who I ran into. It's Matthew.

01:37:08.508 --> 01:37:10.510
Matthew, Alex.

01:37:10.593 --> 01:37:12.595
Finally you two meet.

01:37:21.979 --> 01:37:23.231
Hi.

01:37:24.232 --> 01:37:25.382
Hello.

01:37:26.359 --> 01:37:27.527
Have a seat.

01:37:33.616 --> 01:37:34.784
Hi.

01:37:34.867 --> 01:37:36.285
Hello.

01:37:36.369 --> 01:37:37.519
Want a cocktail?

01:37:38.538 --> 01:37:39.688
Excuse me.

01:37:41.332 --> 01:37:42.583
Hi, how can I help you?

01:37:42.667 --> 01:37:43.835
What do you want?

01:37:43.876 --> 01:37:46.796
A vodka rocks. Double.

01:37:47.463 --> 01:37:48.548
Wow.

01:37:48.631 --> 01:37:49.781
Baby?

01:37:50.883 --> 01:37:53.511
You know what? I'll have, um,

01:37:53.553 --> 01:37:56.431
Put it in a bucket. Not like a double,

01:37:56.514 --> 01:37:58.641
He knows how to do it.
Thanks.

01:37:58.725 --> 01:37:59.767
You got it.

01:37:59.851 --> 01:38:01.561
So what happened
with your psycho?

01:38:04.647 --> 01:38:07.817
You can say it in front of Alex.
She knows the whole story anyway.

01:38:12.071 --> 01:38:14.449
Sometimes when you see
someone from afar...

01:38:16.075 --> 01:38:17.744
you develop a fantasy.

01:38:20.913 --> 01:38:22.331
Then when you see them up close,

01:38:22.415 --> 01:38:24.709
nine times out of ten,

01:38:28.921 --> 01:38:32.467
I have no idea
what you're talking about.

01:38:35.762 --> 01:38:39.182
I was confused,

01:38:40.141 --> 01:38:46.314
thought I'd find what I was looking for,
but I found something else.

01:38:48.107 --> 01:38:49.275
Did you talk to her?

01:38:50.359 --> 01:38:53.279
Just long enough for her
to convince me that she's a liar.

01:38:54.614 --> 01:38:56.199
No harm, no foul, though, right?

01:38:58.534 --> 01:39:01.537
What do you think, Alex?
I mean, you know the whole story.

01:39:04.123 --> 01:39:06.209
It's easy to stand back and judge.

01:39:06.292 --> 01:39:09.003
You don't know anything
about this woman.

01:39:09.754 --> 01:39:13.674
I know that she has no conscience
and no regard for anyone but herself.

01:39:13.758 --> 01:39:15.343
I mean, what else do I need to know?

01:39:15.426 --> 01:39:17.845
You make yourself
into such a victim.

01:39:17.929 --> 01:39:21.015
Nobody made you be with her. You can't
even see what a hypocrite you're being.

01:39:21.099 --> 01:39:22.767
I'm being a hypocrite?
How am I being a hypocrite?

01:39:22.809 --> 01:39:24.685
- Yes, you are!
- Whoa, whoa, whoa.

01:39:24.769 --> 01:39:26.104
You guys. Hey, relax.

01:39:26.187 --> 01:39:27.522
No, Luke. Hey, hold on.

01:39:27.605 --> 01:39:30.483
Alex, I'd like you to explain to me
how I'm being a hypocrite.

01:39:34.278 --> 01:39:39.617
Who's to say this woman hasn't been
in love with you for a really long time?

01:39:39.659 --> 01:39:44.247
And now that she found you again,
she wasn't about to let you go twice.

01:39:47.041 --> 01:39:48.126
What?

01:39:48.167 --> 01:39:49.317
Maybe...

01:39:49.377 --> 01:39:51.212
the first time she saw you,

01:39:51.295 --> 01:39:54.465
maybe she felt the way you did
the first time you saw Lisa.

01:39:55.883 --> 01:39:57.135
You remember that.

01:39:58.761 --> 01:40:01.222
Love makes you do crazy things.

01:40:02.056 --> 01:40:03.516
Insane things.

01:40:04.684 --> 01:40:07.687
Things in a million years
you never thought you'd see yourself do.

01:40:10.064 --> 01:40:12.650
There you are doin' it.
Can't help it.

01:40:13.693 --> 01:40:16.821
Jesus Christ.
Lighten up, you guys.

01:40:16.904 --> 01:40:20.074
This woman... she's a nut.
She's psycho.

01:40:20.158 --> 01:40:23.119
She's cuckoo-bananas, all right?
End of story.

01:40:23.202 --> 01:40:25.329
Can we change the subject?

01:40:25.371 --> 01:40:27.457
I actually have something
to cheer you up.

01:40:27.540 --> 01:40:31.461
Did you, uh, leave a note
with the bartender here a few days ago?

01:40:32.420 --> 01:40:34.172
Yeah, I did.

01:40:34.213 --> 01:40:35.548
'Cause Lisa called.

01:40:36.215 --> 01:40:37.383
What?

01:40:37.467 --> 01:40:42.346
Yeah! After you got off the phone.
She said to meet her at 3:00.

01:40:42.388 --> 01:40:46.017
She couldn't wait long, 'cause she had
to get on a plane to London.

01:40:47.435 --> 01:40:49.562
W-where am I
supposed to meet her?

01:40:49.645 --> 01:40:51.689
She didn't say.
She said you'd know.

01:40:52.523 --> 01:40:53.983
You don't know?

01:40:55.318 --> 01:40:57.195
I think you know where.

01:40:57.236 --> 01:40:58.946
It hasn't been that long, has it?

01:40:59.030 --> 01:41:00.198
What?

01:41:01.199 --> 01:41:03.659
You know, uh...

01:41:04.494 --> 01:41:06.204
Maybe he'll know something.

01:41:08.915 --> 01:41:10.750
You knew she was here
the whole time?

01:41:21.094 --> 01:41:23.054
This belongs to you.

01:41:23.096 --> 01:41:24.722
It's from her.

01:41:38.277 --> 01:41:42.865
"Matt. Please don't think
that I'm running away from you.

01:41:42.949 --> 01:41:46.160
"I was so overwhelmed
when you asked me to move in.

01:41:46.244 --> 01:41:48.413
"I couldn't speak.

01:41:48.454 --> 01:41:51.290
"My answer. Of course. Is yes.

01:41:51.374 --> 01:41:54.419
I love you.
And can't wait to come home."

01:41:57.922 --> 01:42:00.258
I'm not going to apologize
for what I've done.

01:42:03.761 --> 01:42:05.722
This is for me to live with now.

01:42:10.727 --> 01:42:12.729
Now you see me for who I am.

01:42:20.903 --> 01:42:22.613
Yes, I do.

01:42:33.833 --> 01:42:35.001
Hey. Where you goin'?

01:42:35.084 --> 01:42:36.252
Hey.

01:42:36.335 --> 01:42:37.795
Where you goin'?

01:42:37.879 --> 01:42:39.380
I know where she is.

01:42:40.214 --> 01:42:41.883
All right.
Tell me what happens.

01:42:43.676 --> 01:42:46.804
That guy. He's um...

01:42:46.888 --> 01:42:49.140
more drama
than a Mexican soap opera.

01:42:49.182 --> 01:42:51.976
Luke! This...

01:42:52.060 --> 01:42:53.227
This is over.

01:42:53.311 --> 01:42:54.771
- What's over?
- Us.

01:42:56.564 --> 01:42:58.566
How can it be over?
We haven't even started yet.

01:42:58.649 --> 01:43:00.318
I'm not who you think I am.

01:43:01.694 --> 01:43:02.987
I used you.

01:43:18.169 --> 01:43:19.319
Taxi!

01:43:20.671 --> 01:43:21.821
Come on.

01:43:35.937 --> 01:43:37.087
Hey!

01:43:38.064 --> 01:43:39.565
Hey, come on!

01:43:40.274 --> 01:43:42.235
God!

01:43:46.239 --> 01:43:47.389
Hey!

01:43:49.409 --> 01:43:51.160
Hey! Hey!

01:43:55.248 --> 01:43:56.416
Sorry.

01:43:56.499 --> 01:43:57.542
Thanks.

01:43:57.625 --> 01:43:59.794
- Goin' to Wicker Park.
- Yeah, right away.

01:45:01.189 --> 01:45:02.857
Your attention. Please.

01:45:02.940 --> 01:45:06.277
Flight 862 service to London
is now boarding.

01:45:33.179 --> 01:45:34.329
Hi!

01:45:35.598 --> 01:45:37.433
There you are!

01:45:37.517 --> 01:45:40.478
Where've you been?
Your flight got in an hour ago.

01:45:40.561 --> 01:45:42.397
I've been down
to luggage claim and back.

01:45:43.731 --> 01:45:45.233
- Rebecca.
- Hey.

01:45:45.316 --> 01:45:46.526
I, um...

01:45:46.609 --> 01:45:48.236
What's the matter?

01:45:48.319 --> 01:45:49.862
Rough flight home?

01:45:49.946 --> 01:45:52.365
Did you bring me back
that little Chinese dress?

01:45:56.202 --> 01:45:57.995
- Rebecca...
- You okay, Sweetie?

01:45:59.747 --> 01:46:01.207
I didn't go to China.

01:46:03.292 --> 01:46:04.669
What are you talking about?

01:46:04.752 --> 01:46:07.839
Hi, Alex. You're never gonna
believe what happened.

01:46:07.922 --> 01:46:09.674
Matthew's back in town.

01:46:11.217 --> 01:46:12.718
I can't marry you.

01:46:13.678 --> 01:46:15.346
It would be a huge mistake.

01:46:15.388 --> 01:46:18.057
You're gonna have to help me out, baby.
Did I do something wrong?

01:46:18.141 --> 01:46:21.018
No, you didn't...
You didn't do anything wrong.

01:46:21.102 --> 01:46:22.252
Rebecca, I...

01:46:23.479 --> 01:46:26.315
I've been doing something wrong
for the last two years.

01:46:27.150 --> 01:46:29.736
I'm not...
I'm not this person.

01:46:29.819 --> 01:46:32.155
I can't go back with you.
I can't do this.

01:46:32.739 --> 01:46:35.241
I was gonna meet him in the park,
but he didn't show up.

01:46:36.284 --> 01:46:38.578
Yeah... I know.

01:46:38.661 --> 01:46:39.996
What do you mean?

01:46:40.079 --> 01:46:45.376
Lisa. I've been doing some really...
horrible and selfish things.

01:46:45.460 --> 01:46:47.211
What are you talking about?

01:46:47.253 --> 01:46:49.380
I've been keeping you apart.

01:46:49.422 --> 01:46:52.633
When we met two years ago,
I was in love with someone else.

01:46:52.717 --> 01:46:55.720
And she just came back
into my life.

01:46:56.471 --> 01:46:59.057
She broke my heart...
And I'm sorry!

01:46:59.640 --> 01:47:00.975
Oh, my God.

01:47:06.773 --> 01:47:09.650
I... Rebecca, I know...

01:47:09.734 --> 01:47:11.569
I know that I'm still in love with her.

01:47:12.361 --> 01:47:14.363
I just... I needed you to know.

01:47:15.156 --> 01:47:16.491
Know what?

01:47:17.617 --> 01:47:19.619
Know what, Matthew?

01:47:20.912 --> 01:47:22.955
That I'm not the girl
that can break your heart?

